Path: godot/tutorials/math/vector_math.rst
Summary: Demonstrates how to calculate a vector pointing from one position to another.
To find a vector pointing from A to B, use B - A. In this scenario, you have a tank that wishes to point its turret at a robot. Subtracting the tank's position from the robot's position gives the vector pointing from the tank to the robot.
